oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Martha Elizabeth Lucy Grimes Milliken tintype
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Tintype of Martha "Mattie" Elizabeth Lucy Grimes Milliken. She was born in 1866 in Giles Coiunty, Tennessee. She married James Alexander "Alec" Cathey Milliken on April 5, 1902, in Linocln County, Tennessee. She died in Lincoln County in 1928. James Alexander "Alec" Cathey Milliken (April 3, 1836-September 20, 1920), Co. K, 1st Tenn. Inf. (Turney's) Regt., CSA. He was detailed as a medical sergeant under Dr. Calvin McGuire and worked in this capacity during the Second Battle of Manassas.
